snippet.textDisplay:
This video was all about who Zohaib Kazi is. It reflects him, his personality, his work and his taste of music. From Butter Fly in Space to Zoe & Zohaib and all those sideline projects he did while keeping a day job st CS and to his long awaited graphic album Ismail Ka Shehre is a piece of art. And then came his collaboration with Patari that resulted in breathtaking journey Fanoos, that allowed him to take CS to similar journey... my only fear was will this work, people failed Rohail for his unique CS6, but Kazi had the edge of Fanoos, as people loved that work, he knew they will love it too. Also thi is a pre-season treat or epilogue or explorer or whatever you call it, is an insight of what is coming in regular season. But I hope that crisp and anticipation remains intact otherwise it is doomed.

I am already loving it, people will have a hard time accepting this if same thing came in regular setup. For me this was amazing! 4/5

Ps: As this was whole Kazi, Ali's vision seems to be missing completely. I hope we get to see him equally in next episodes.
